title: Baked butternut squash with garlic and cheese
ingredients: ['2 tablespoons finely chopped fresh parsley', '1 teaspoon herbes de Provence', '2 tablespoons olive oil', '3 garlic cloves, minced', '1 teaspoon salt', 'ground black pepper to taste', '1.5kg butternut squash, peeled and diced', '50g grated Parmesan cheese']
